04:15.342 --> 04:17.125
Oh, I would want.
That would be great.

04:17.168 --> 04:18.649
Yes, please. Please, yes.

04:18.692 --> 04:20.695
So you can see why
this matters to me.

04:20.738 --> 04:21.738
He's a genius.

04:21.783 --> 04:23.393
Yeah. He is.

04:23.437 --> 04:24.588
I mean, he's always had issues,

04:24.612 --> 04:26.788
